DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T2.id AS id, T1.GroupingId, T1.DiscountingCurvesId, T1.YieldCurvesId, T1.IndexForwardingCurvesId, T1.SwapIndexCurvesId, T1.ZeroInflationIndexCurvesId, T1.YYInflationIndexCurvesId, T1.FxSpotsId, T1.FxVolatilitiesId, T1.SwaptionVolatilitiesId, T1.CapFloorVolatilitiesId, T1.CDSVolatilitiesId, T1.DefaultCurvesId, T1.InflationCapFloorPriceSurfacesId, T1.EquityCurvesId, T1.EquityVolatilitiesId FROM ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketConfiguration T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketConfigurationTypes T2 ON T1.id = T2.id

field.name: *id
field.lookup: SELECT id,id lookup FROM ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketConfigurationTypes ORDER BY id
